about.summary: Standalone version of django.utils.feedgenerator, compatible with Py3k

name: feedgenerator
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.9" %}

package:
  name: feedgenerator
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/f/feedgenerator/feedgenerator-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5ae05daa9cfa47fa406ee4744d0b7fa1c8a05a7a47ee0ad328ddf55327cfb106

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - pytz
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - feedgenerator
    - feedgenerator.django
    - feedgenerator.django.utils

about:
  home: https://github.com/dmdm/feedgenerator-py3k.git
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  summary: Standalone version of django.utils.feedgenerator, compatible with Py3k

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - moorepants
